  "title": "Digital Marketing Sales Executive #80974",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Web Design & Development Agency</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Digital Marketing Sales Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Hybrid – Central office or WFH</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Mon-Fri: 9am to 6pm or 10am to 7pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 3500 + Monthly/ Quarterly Commission</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Promote company's services, including Web Development, SEO, SEM, and Social Media Marketing</li><li>Able to develop new business opportunities, manage existing clients, and prepare proposals/quotations</li><li>Capable of liaising with the in-house technical team for pre-sales clarifications</li><li>Ensure a smooth handover of clients to the project team after sales closure</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. ITE in Marketing, Business or a related study</li><li>Min. 1 year of working experience in a digital marketing agency</li><li>Knowledge of Canva is an added advantage</li><li>Able to work independently</li><li>Strong communication and organisational skills</li><li>Basic understanding of web development and digital marketing, with the ability to provide value-added suggestions during client discussions</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80974 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
